snippet.title: Blocksworld Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Blocksworld Kickstarter Trailer for the main page

---
Want to see more Blocksworld videos? SUBSCRIBE to our channel! https://www.youtube.com/c/BlocksworldGame

Welcome to Blocksworld, a fun 3D-building game for the whole family! Drag and snap building blocks together to make anything from cute characters to mighty machines.

More from Blocksworld: 
Official Blocksworld Website: https://www.roblox.com/
Blocksworld Merch store https://blocksworld.myspreadshop.com/
